beer.beer_description: Big on its hop aromas and has moderate bitterness. We use Cascade and Amarillo hops with Cascades late in the boil, and also dry hopping in the fermenter. Victorville has a citrus flavour profile with a pronounced grapefruit amd a touch of passionfruit. A prefect cleanser after that big heavy red or heavy real ale.
